Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,強姦隔壁姐姐 的那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，我是隔壁新搬來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫彩月\N這個不怎麼貴重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今後請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,特意的準備\N真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是個很有趣的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我從中介那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這個公寓是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒\N不是，與其說是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我爺爺的，我爺爺是總醫院的院長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒，那你也是醫生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有考上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能考上醫學部我覺得\N很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我這個笨蛋，說了很多奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得擁有理想，並為之努力的人很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,超級厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不會那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,本來只是想打個招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,今後也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有理想，並為之努力的人很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我很羨慕你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾完了\N剛靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很想明天到公司，好好地跟你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也有東西帶給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要出差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,下周來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會有點寂寞\N我會忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那再聯絡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要出去嗎？\N那一起去地鐵站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以嗎？  -當然\N不快走的話就遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月，和我這樣的人一起走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不會啊，你要對自己有信心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎？\N一定要有自信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,像你這樣溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只要在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是，只要有你 在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月，歡迎回來\N怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你在學習\N打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,經過超市的時候買的\N覺得可以做夜宵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,請用\N彩月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我會為了報答你對我的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好好努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦\N那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,還在工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他說了會打電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N難道你快遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢，昨天怎麼都睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話我來幫你扔垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思\N沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不快點的話，會遲到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝，像你這樣溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,超級喜歡\N我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,山田，怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N難得的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我家裡給我寄來了櫻桃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就給你拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻桃很難得的\N謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,進來吧\N一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,跟一個人吃相比，兩個人一起吃會很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,進來，進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，那打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，真害羞\N不要那樣看，很亂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,山田，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,山田，不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的，這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭舔下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,進來了，看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢，彩月\N看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.94,0:24:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,硬邦邦的\N怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.28,0:24:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多喜歡你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要幹我，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.79,0:24:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.47,0:25:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.34,0:25:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出去，不要強姦我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.22,0:25:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全部插進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.62,0:25:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.23,0:25:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.79,0:26:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.73,0:26:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.31,0:26:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,都是大人了，知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.91,0:26:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.51,0:27:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.73,0:28:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要幹了  不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.87,0:28:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不要幹我　好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.34,0:28:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N我射了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.28,0:28:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不能射進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.66,0:29:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.94,0:29:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.61,0:29:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這個就當做是 我們兩個人的秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.55,0:29:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩個之間 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.82,0:29:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就像現在這樣，是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.16,0:30:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.74,0:30:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.56,0:31:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.30,0:31:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.46,0:31:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.93,0:31:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.14,0:31:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.14,0:31:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.62,0:32:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的午飯吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.09,0:32:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一直吃飯的地方\N怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.30,0:32:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,領帶歪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.77,0:32:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.40,0:33:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.62,0:33:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.22,0:33:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰啊\N那個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.03,0:33:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.37,0:33:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說好了 兩個人之間的秘密嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.91,0:33:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很喜歡我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.80,0:33:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,和那個男人相比，更喜歡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.27,0:34:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.07,0:34:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,總是很會照顧人的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.88,0:34:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼溫柔的山田，去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.08,0:34:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,首先背叛我的是 誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.43,0:34:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.50,0:34:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.78,0:34:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,換上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.19,0:35:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的面前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.87,0:35:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道傷害我 有多深嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.67,0:35:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.95,0:35:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.15,0:35:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不聽我說的，我會做很怪的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.96,0:35:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了，我換
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.56,0:35:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我換
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.84,0:35:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡磨蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.71,0:35:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我會好好拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.52,0:36:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.81,0:36:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男人也看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.96,0:36:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.23,0:36:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我會換的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.66,0:37:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.14,0:37:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要那麼的近
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.74,0:37:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以說那樣的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.01,0:37:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個寄到公司吧\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.62,0:37:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.69,0:37:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.17,0:37:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這個衣服 很適合你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.99,0:38:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,身體真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.43,0:38:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要寄到我公司
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.37,0:39:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那要看你怎麼表現了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.24,0:39:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.12,0:39:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,會分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.86,0:39:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我會寄的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.34,0:39:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,寄送的話會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.36,0:39:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N換完了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.76,0:40:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲也脫下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.03,0:40:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真是 什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.44,0:40:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.85,0:40:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我會發信息給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.92,0:40:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.80,0:40:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你發信息
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.53,0:40:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,說老公
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.34,0:40:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我寄送了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.14,0:40:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.41,0:40:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不管什麼 命令我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.15,0:41:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不管什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.49,0:41:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,命令我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.85,0:41:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,乳尖出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.12,0:41:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼害羞的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.53,0:41:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上這樣的衣服，很害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.21,0:42:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.32,0:42:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.72,0:42:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,走過來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.60,0:42:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了這樣的 事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.61,0:43:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,轉一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.30,0:43:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.12,0:43:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.80,0:44:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕我這麼溫柔的老公嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.84,0:44:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.51,0:44:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.12,0:44:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.73,0:45:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人來製作更多的甜蜜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.53,0:46:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,表情這樣的話，衣服就浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.55,0:46:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.90,0:46:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.70,0:46:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.67,0:48:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.30,0:49:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,射了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.58,0:49:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.72,0:49:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.06,0:49:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊\N舔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.27,0:49:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你要說老公，讓我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.88,0:49:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.48,0:49:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.91,0:50:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再用點心
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.38,0:50:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.05,0:50:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,超級喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.59,0:50:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,超級喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.60,0:50:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,跟狗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.41,0:50:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.49,0:51:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,會聽我的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.64,0:51:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再弄得水水的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.72,0:51:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,發出點噁心的聲音，給我興奮下
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.32,0:51:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,邊舔邊出聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.86,0:51:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,用伺候自己老公的態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.09,0:53:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我會叫你更爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.76,0:53:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓你更爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.57,0:53:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自己把雞巴放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.70,0:53:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,搖著你的屁股坐下來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.31,0:53:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.53,0:54:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,進來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.94,0:54:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,自己該說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.74,0:54:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.14,0:54:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的雞巴
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.48,0:54:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,每個細節都要報告哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.29,0:54:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴在屄裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.76,0:54:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在我屄裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.97,0:54:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的雞巴
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.84,0:54:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,自己搖屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.06,0:54:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不問一下老公是不是 很爽之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.76,0:55:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雞巴插得爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.59,0:55:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.21,0:55:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,叫老公
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.82,0:55:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，你爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.55,0:55:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再噁心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.09,0:55:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.22,0:55:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹我幹得爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.16,0:55:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.54,0:56:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽\N喂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.28,0:56:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.75,0:56:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，很好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.29,0:56:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.44,0:56:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不是分手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.51,0:57:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和他分手
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.32,0:57:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和他說你有老公了，要和他分手
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.46,0:57:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.67,0:57:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.88,0:57:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,還在拖什麼？想我去散照片嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.35,0:57:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我有話要對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.69,0:57:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.03,0:57:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,請和我分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.10,0:57:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,說你老公的雞巴正在操你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.71,0:58:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我新老公的雞巴
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.65,0:58:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,正在操我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.85,0:58:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.06,0:58:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我會愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.06,0:58:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的女人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.06,0:59:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們生個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.06,0:59:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.06,0:59:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要懷你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.06,0:59:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要對我做那麼殘忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.06,0:59:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,由不得你不要
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.06,0:59:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你注定要懷我的種
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.06,0:59:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,替我生兒育女
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.06,0:59:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.56,0:59:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,準備大肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.06,0:59:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你想生男的還是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.06,0:59:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,男的還是女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.36,0:59:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,說老公，我願意生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快說！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.36,0:59:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.36,0:59:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我願意生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.36,0:59:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我情願一輩子生你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.32,1:00:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我情願
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.42,1:00:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一輩子為你生孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.42,1:00:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就得為幸福的家庭努力了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.42,1:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你的女兒，將來一起伺候老公
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.42,1:01:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.42,1:01:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.42,1:01:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼大的奶子
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.42,1:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,巨乳唷
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.00,1:02:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,將來女兒也是巨乳
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.42,1:02:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,巨乳光榮嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.59,1:02:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,問我爽不爽？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.89,1:02:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.96,1:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,敬語\N您爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.31,1:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跟誰說呢\N老公
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.38,1:02:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.83,1:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.65,1:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把你操很爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.06,1:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,發出聲音來
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.80,1:04:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽了，忍不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.08,1:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,發出聲音來
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.91,1:04:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.52,1:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快點要老公獎勵你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.27,1:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老公請獎勵我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.07,1:05:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想要大肚生孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.08,1:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想大肚生孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.02,1:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,算了，這次便宜你，射臉上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.02,1:05:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再玩我了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.02,1:05:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不射臉上，這次就真的要受孕了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.00,1:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還不求我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.49,1:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,請把獎勵射在我臉上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.03,1:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請把獎勵射在我臉上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.04,1:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,叫老公
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.90,1:05:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.51,1:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.00,1:06:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.43,1:06:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.46,1:08:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 那樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.06,1:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你就這般討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.00,1:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,笑一下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.68,1:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.35,1:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.48,1:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拿來了禮物
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.76,1:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用這個再做一個「兩個人的記憶」吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.10,1:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.17,1:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.71,1:09:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,自已把裙子捲起來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.31,1:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我好好的看看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.85,1:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.13,1:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是看不見的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.54,1:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,還要
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.28,1:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,穿的內褲不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.29,1:09:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.76,1:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.63,1:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為了可以放進去，自己做點準備工作
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.04,1:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.71,1:10:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不快點做的話，會來人的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.69,1:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快點脫下來
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.63,1:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.25,1:11:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.14,1:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,早上就這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.08,1:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,其實很開心的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.48,1:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是變態呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.49,1:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那我幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.44,1:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,會來人的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.46,1:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你也會做這麼噁心的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.27,1:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.81,1:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.90,1:13:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以掉出來哦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.64,1:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這個很貴的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.41,1:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是放在這裡的話\N很快就會射的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.29,1:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要掉下來，自己扶著
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.10,1:14:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,請打開
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.04,1:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,請打開
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.46,1:14:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.26,1:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爽嗎\N很爽
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.01,1:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.43,1:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不行了\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.63,1:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.18,1:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,說謊很嚴重的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.50,1:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,會來人的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.12,1:17:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來啊，不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.47,1:17:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.49,1:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.63,1:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不會停止的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.70,1:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.71,1:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.52,1:18:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還差很多呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.46,1:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,會來人的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.07,1:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,會給他們看的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.48,1:18:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要\N忍一下
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.17,1:19:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.66,1:19:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N尿出來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.07,1:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,尿出來
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.47,1:19:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來人了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.61,1:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.16,1:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,放進去嘛\N會很快尿的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.10,1:21:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-喂
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.51,1:21:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不動產嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.35,1:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.35,1:22:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.35,1:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我接到了不動產的電話
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.49,1:22:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,說你在找房間
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.76,1:22:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，我拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.03,1:22:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你，現在開始會
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.44,1:22:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一直和我生活的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.44,1:22:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.64,1:22:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的事情不要再做了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.85,1:22:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會跟任何人說的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.92,1:22:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.79,1:22:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡還要
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.26,1:22:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,製造記憶吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.87,1:22:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.47,1:23:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.15,1:23:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,人生，夢想
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.08,1:23:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不會成功的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.22,1:23:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.16,1:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要放棄人生和理想
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.83,1:23:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,彩月，你還真的是在擔心我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.11,1:23:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的，我只要在這裡一直和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.78,1:23:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就只要那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.23,1:25:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不要呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.03,1:25:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼討厭我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.71,1:25:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我的嗎？\N我聽, 不要這樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.72,1:26:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.53,1:26:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有了喜歡的男人，不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.55,1:26:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭再伸出來，動一下
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.50,1:26:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.31,1:26:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.31,1:27:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心哦，你喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.99,1:27:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.86,1:27:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快，看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.62,1:27:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.22,1:27:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.51,1:29:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.52,1:29:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.26,1:29:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.81,1:29:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.90,1:31:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.11,1:31:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.59,1:31:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.59,1:31:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的，全部喝下去
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.47,1:31:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.28,1:33:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.02,1:33:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好好地聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.83,1:33:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.97,1:33:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快點給我脫下來
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.19,1:33:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.87,1:34:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.16,1:35:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.23,1:35:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,舔啊，舔啊\N全身
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.90,1:35:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,全部舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.25,1:36:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.74,1:36:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.94,1:36:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.08,1:36:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不聽話就這樣了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.81,1:38:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭在裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.55,1:38:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.83,1:38:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭舔
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.97,1:39:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.72,1:39:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做那樣的事情了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.60,1:39:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.13,1:39:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.15,1:39:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,發出那樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.90,1:40:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.31,1:40:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再來 舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.78,1:40:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.39,1:40:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,還很硬呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.86,1:40:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,摸著自己的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.60,1:40:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊手淫
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.87,1:40:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快點手淫啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.48,1:40:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿出來
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.00,1:41:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.14,1:41:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.82,1:42:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,已經濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.31,1:42:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,跟剛才的姿勢一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.78,1:42:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自己把腿張開
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.12,1:42:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大雞巴要來幹小騷屄了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.53,1:42:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要不戴套就插進來
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.68,1:43:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼的爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.23,1:43:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多時間的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.04,1:43:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.18,1:43:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不想死就聽話
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.13,1:44:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以再說 不要之類的話
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.60,1:45:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,說再來\N再來, 再上我
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.56,1:45:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好地聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.43,1:46:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.64,1:46:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.05,1:47:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.42,1:47:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,山田\N看這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.02,1:47:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.24,1:48:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,現在很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.18,1:48:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.25,1:48:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.63,1:49:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你屁股操起來真是帶勁
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.56,1:49:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大屁股一定好生養
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.56,1:49:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我以後　一定　很會生
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.16,1:49:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.36,1:50:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很愛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.36,1:50:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.26,1:50:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我是這樣的表情嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.43,1:50:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是那樣的表情呢\N向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.17,1:50:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.79,1:50:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你忍什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.26,1:50:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,爽嗎？\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.90,1:51:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我看到啥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.70,1:51:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.30,1:51:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到我的屄了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.31,1:51:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到騷屄了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.78,1:51:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看看自己的屄
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.52,1:51:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很興奮吧\N睜大眼睛給我看
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.46,1:51:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看見什麼？\N看見老公在上我
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.14,1:51:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咬住了\N這奶是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.05,1:52:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.12,1:52:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我嗎\N好愛
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.86,1:52:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我嗎？愛老公嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.06,1:52:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,愛老公\N真愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.79,1:52:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,愛老公嗎？\N我愛
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.73,1:52:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真愛老公嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.73,1:52:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再說，再說\N我愛老公，好愛
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.80,1:52:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我就要天天被我上
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.80,1:53:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也來給你下種
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.94,1:54:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.61,1:54:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我更興奮了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.36,1:54:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不要, 不要不要
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.50,1:54:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,山田，不要射進去
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.97,1:54:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要大肚子
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.45,1:54:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要讓我懷孕
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.12,1:54:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有大好前途的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.84,1:55:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以懷孽種的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.25,1:56:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以懷孽種的
